{"title": "World's Great Men of Music: Story-Lives of Master Musicians", "description": "These stories are gathered from many sources including biographies, letters, journals and musical history. The life story of 25 of the most celebrated musicians is presented. The author has aimed to make the story-sketches interesting to young people in hopes that they may prove valuable to musical readers of all ages. Students of piano, violin or other instruments need to know how the great composers lived their lives. In every musical career described in this book, from the old masters represented by Bach and Beethoven to the musical prophets of our own day, there is a wealth of inspiration and practical guidance for the artist in any field. Through their struggles, sorrows and triumphs, divine melody and harmony came into being, which will bless the world for all time to come.  - Summary taken from the Foreword of the author", "duration": 37615, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "15721", "name": "Harriette Brower"}], "coverArt": null, "copyright_year": "1922", "genres": ["Biography & Autobiography", "Music"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Sonia"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Sonia"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Sonia"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Foreword", "readers": [15288], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/worlds_great_men_of_music_2206_librivox/worldsgreatmenofmusic_00_brower_64kb.mp3", "duration": 122}, {"section": 1, "title": "Palestrina", "readers": [15288], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/worlds_great_men_of_music_2206_librivox/worldsgreatmenofmusic_01_brower_64kb.mp3", "duration": 812}, {"section": 2, "title": "John Sebastian Bach", "readers": [15288], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/worlds_great_men_of_music_2206_librivox/worldsgreatmenofmusic_02_brower_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1466}, {"section": 3, "title": "George Frederick Ha